comments: Jackson (PHX) makes marginal contact with Randle (NOP) in the post.
Bender (PHX) makes contact to Randle's (NOP) body during his shooting motion.
Clark (NOP) briefly places a hand/arm to the front of Melton (PHX) during the drive.
Wood (NOP) cleanly blocks Melton's (PHX) driving shot attempt.
Randle (NOP) is firming up and makes marginal contact with Melton (PHX) after the dribble hand-off.
Bender (PHX) retreats and brings his arms to a legal position, making incidental contact with Randle (NOP) during his shot attempt.
After the pick, Bender (NOP) extends his arms into Payton (NOP) and affects his defensive position.
Payton (NOP) makes incidental contact to the off-arm of Crawford (PHX) that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Randle (NOP) takes fewer than three steps after he has gathered the ball.
Bender (PHX) makes clean contact with the ball and any ensuing contact to Randle's (NOP) arm is deemed incidental.
Wood (NOP) has his arm extended and makes incidental contact with Crawford (PHX) during the loose ball.
Randle (NOP) has a resting arm on Bridges' (PHX) body during his shooting motion that does not affect his driving shot attempt.
Jackson (PHX) makes contact to Randle's (NOP) arm that affects his SQBR.
Hill (NOP) and Bender (PHX) briefly engage and disengage during the rebound.

Coach Kokoskov (PHX) walks onto the court and illegally requests a timeout when his team does not have control of the basketball.  A technical foul is whistled when the Pelicans do have possession of the ball and they are awarded one free throw and maintain possession.
Bender (PHX) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Randle (NOP) and the shot is cleanly blocked by Melton (PHX).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the floor of Suns possession is overturned to Pelicans possession.
[Observable in enhanced video] Payton (NOP) does not release the inbound pass within five seconds.
Bender (PHX) makes incidental contact to the body of Hill (NOP) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Williams (NOP) commits a take foul on Crawford (PHX).
Hill (NOP) and Crawford (PHX) engage and disengage during the inbound.
